thread.title_full: Car Hire Labs bewertet von Richard

author: Richard
title: Richard
text: The best rate I could find before using CareHireLabs was 40% off the normal web rate. CarHireLabs had a rate that was 70% off which was ridiculously low and I was so skeptical I almost did not book it but the reviews seemed to show it was legitimate. After booking it, I contacted the car rental company directly to see if my reservation was there, they confirmed it was there and they also verified my low rate. I am really impressed!
